# Compiled TypeScript output should only ever live in dist/.
# If a stray `tsc` invocation ever drops .js/.d.ts next to a .ts source
# under src/, do not let it sneak into a commit — Node's ESM loader
# rejects CJS-emitted siblings of "type": "module" files.
src/**/*.js
src/**/*.js.map
src/**/*.d.ts
src/**/*.d.ts.map
